Title: Principal Bundles, Connections and BRST Cohomology

Authors: H. Garc\' \I A-Compe\' an, J.M. L\' opez-Romero, M.A. Rodr\' \I

guez-Segura and M. SocolovskyComments: 31 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Aport. Mat. Com. 13, 63-94, 1993

We review the elementary theory of gauge fields and the Becchi-Rouet-Stora-Tyutin symmetry in the context of differential geometry. We emphasize thetopological nature of this symmetry and discuss a double Chevalley-Eilenbergcomplex for it.